__pycache__/
.venv/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
uv.lock

# The synced quern package cache is COMMITTED, not ignored. quern.lock is still the source of
# truth — it names each package by digest — but ignoring the bytes it names meant CI had to
# fetch them, from xag/quern-registry, which is frozen at ledger@0.4.1. So the suite died on
# "ledger@0.5.0 (pinned) is not in the library" from the repin onward. The package is data;
# it travels with the lock, and a registry only refreshes it.
